commit caf759f72fdf78340dadbf62cf00c3c00c8a5b0e
Author: Emmanuele Bassi <ebassi@gnome.org>
Date:   Wed Feb 29 09:24:34 2012 +0000

    interactive: Remove test-actor-clone
    
