Date:   Tue Jan 31 10:23:48 2012 +0000

    texture: It's bytes per pixel, not bits
    
    Clarify the error message when checking the bpp argument.

 clutter/clutter-texture.c |   20 ++++++++++----------
 1 file changed, 10 insertions(+), 10 deletions(-)

